data.text:
Steven Pinto-Borges is a French football player born on March 26, 1986, in Vitry-sur-Seine, France. He plays as a midfielder and has represented the Portuguese national under-21 team. Throughout his career, he has played for several clubs including Cherbourg, Guingamp, Grenoble, and Clermont 63.
